  "title": "Factory Reception & Attendant",
  "description": "<p>Location: Gul Drive (West Area)<br>\n<br>\nWorking Hours:<br>\n<br>\nDay Shift: 8:00 AM – 8:30 PM (1.5 hrs meal break)<br>\n<br>\nNight Shift: 8:00 PM – 8:30 AM (1.5 hrs meal break)<br>\n<br>\nShift Overlap: 8:00 – 8:30 (30 mins handover)<br>\n<br>\nRest Days: 4 days per month<br>\n<br>\nJob Responsibilities:<br>\n<br>\nFront Desk Registration: Record entry and exit details of vehicles and visitors.<br>\n<br>\nSimple Patrols: Conduct routine walkarounds to ensure cleanliness and proper functioning of facilities.<br>\n<br>\nNight Duty: Perform gatekeeping and logging duties during night shifts as scheduled.<br>\n<br>\nFactory Environment Upkeep: Maintain cleanliness of main areas and assist with light landscaping tasks.<br>\n<br>\nGeneral Support: Assist management with daily operational or administrative tasks as required.<br>\n<br>\nJob Requirements:<br>\n<br>\nNo Security Officer license required.<br>\n<br>\nAble to work rotating shifts, including night shifts.<br>\n<br>\nResponsible and able to work independently.<br>\n<br>\nPreferably with experience in factory operations, facility maintenance, or cleaning duties.<br>\n<br>\nSuitable for individuals looking for a stable, long-term role.<br>\n<br>\nLEE LAI MUN<br>\nR1657696</p>",
